responses: {"Q0":"There was an attempt to figure out a pattern at first, then I reasoned that the more 'observe outcome' buttons I chose, the less chances there would be to earn any amount of points. So I tried to give somewhat equal amounts of choices to both the red and blue balls. \n\nWith the orange and purple boxes, I chose boxes that had higher chances of picking up an orange. When the chances were close to 1/2 I'd gamble on the random box. "}
